divs: Sighting DetailsI went out my back door to have cigaette, looked up and saw a chinese-type lntern thing with a long string attached, dangling below it, with lights as well. There was a plane-like object on the same trajectory that dissapeared at the same time the lantern-thing vanished. The Airplane-ish object was clearly much higher than the lantern-ish obeject, though after they vanished, other airplanes were flying in a normal flight line. It happened very fast, maybe 30 to 45 seconds.
Summary: Chinese-type lantern with dangling line and higher elevated fireball entity following.
